Package ispd.arquivo.xml.models.builders

Class CloudQueueNetworkParser

java.lang.Object
ispd.arquivo.xml.models.builders.GridQueueNetworkParser
ispd.arquivo.xml.models.builders.CloudQueueNetworkParser
public class CloudQueueNetworkParser extends GridQueueNetworkParser
Class to build a cloud queue network from a model in a WrappedDocument. The usage is the same as in GridQueueNetworkParser.
